rows.label: bf06060100_0010
rows.name:
What a spectacle... Seems the Pope has
as much clout around here as ever.

rows.label: bf06060100_0020
rows.name:
Could we not just take
them out here and now?

rows.label: bf06060100_0030
rows.name:
Good point. All the principal
nations' heads gathered here...

rows.label: bf06060100_0040
rows.name:
The way to the World Tree
must first be opened.

rows.label: bf06060100_0050
rows.name:
Wiping out mankind is the easy part.
We could manage that ourselves.

rows.label: bf06060100_0070
rows.name:
That isn't our only goal, remember? We
must wait for the stage to be set.

rows.label: bf06060100_0090
rows.name: Yeah, I've been wondering that myself...

rows.label: bf06060100_0100
rows.name: Heh. Oh, he's serious. He always is.
